

	yat directly code run kelya natar 404 error yeto ye so to yeto means he spring MVC + security properly
	intergrate nahi hot so aapn jo HomeControlle madhe URL write kela ye to 'register' to directly open
	kara y cha Browser URL Address bar madhe
	   
	initially asa asto --> http://localhost:7000/SpringSecurityRegistration  - ya la error yeto 404 mang 
	this one  -->  http://localhost:7000/SpringSecurityRegistration/register
	
	@Configuration
	public class SecurityConfig {

    @Bean 
    public PasswordEncoder passwordEncoder() {
        return new BCryptPasswordEncoder();
    }
}

	this is the PasswordEncoder class using this we can Encrypte password and Decrypte password this class 
	is same in both  spring MVC + Boot  we have method 
-->  String encrypted = passwordEncoder.encode(user.getPassword());
		user.setPassword(encrypted);
		
		to encrypte user password menas ya cha use kela k auser cha password DB madhde store hota na 
		$2a$10$Vd7D.sDKSb7lWmx1vQpErOGo2l/l4Y7Er841g0.lwoGnbW8Kj0cRu   hya format madhe store hoto 
		which provide a security to us 
		
main methods of the PasswordEncoder class : 
1. encode(CharSecuence password) --> Store password in encrypted format plane password store hot nahi and 
		disAdvan--> encrypted password long asto
		
2. matches(CharSequence rawPassword, String encodedPassword) : Login veles check karto password correct 
		aahe ka.

Mostly used EncoderClasses : 
	1. BCryptPasswordEncoder  --> storng hashing 
	2. Pbkdf2PasswordEncoder  --> High Security hasing used in banking / security app
	3. SCryptPasswordEncoder  --> Advanced HAsing 
